B) Commercial Use

You must purchase a license if:

· You are a museum, gallery, cultural institution, or company that charges entry fees or generates revenue using this software.
· You are using it in a funded project (public or private).

💳 Licensing Fees

· One-time license: €11,000 (permanent use for one project/exhibition)
· Annual license: €3,000/year (unlimited projects within one institution)

